item.title: Trying to delete skills :S +rep!
item.dc:creator: @purestmage74 purestmage74
item.description:
@purestmage74 wrote:

Things he probably done:

Added character-file writing for it.
(It saves in the characters file: Pking skill = ?)

Replaced the sprites.
(In the cache you can replace the pking icon with what you want it to be)

Possibly replaced another skill.
(yes, maybe removed summoning/ rewrote?)

Check all the skills you know of that don’t refer to a packet, than search through Player.java or Client.java maybe even PlayerAssistant.java , try removing every case of it AS LONG AS you know it isn’t something major, or isn’t needed for another purpose.

hope it helps.
